description: Gets the status of a data set import task initiated with the  CreateDataSetImportTask operation.

parameters.name: taskId
parameters.description: The task identifier returned by the  CreateDataSetImportTask operation.

nested_items.name: failed
nested_items.description: The number of data set imports that have failed.

nested_items.name: inProgress
nested_items.description: The number of data set imports that are in progress.

nested_items.name: pending
nested_items.description: The number of data set imports that are pending.

nested_items.name: succeeded
nested_items.description: The number of data set imports that have succeeded.

nested_items.name: total
nested_items.description: The total number of data set imports.
